{{Quote|When an enemy corvette jumped into the area, I wasted no time: We had been warned in our briefing that this was a particularly dangerous CRV, a prototype of some kind, and I decided I didn't want to know what tricks it had up its metallic sleeve.|[[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Farlander's]] [[After-action report/Legends|After-Action Report]]|<ref name="X-Wing Collector's CD-ROM: The Official Strategy Guide">''[[X-Wing Collector's CD-ROM: The Official Strategy Guide]]''</ref>}}
'''''Assassin 1''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]]. It was sent to destroy a container full of [[Grain/Legends|grain]] that was earlier dropped in haste to escape an ambush and then sent to be picked up again. The ''Assassin 1'', however was destroyed by [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] ace [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]].

